  <tmpl:var name="title">Register to Vote in Massachusetts</tmpl:var>
  <tmpl:var name="content">
    <h2>Register to Vote</h2>
    <p>Massachusetts currently does not have a statewide voter registration system that allows online voter registration. You can either request a <a href="http://www.sec.state.ma.us/ele/elestu/stuidx.htm">mail-in voter registration form from the Massachusetts Secretary of State</a> or download and print out a <a href="http://www.eac.gov/docs/nvra.pdf">National Voter Registration form</a>. The <a href="http://www.eac.gov/docs/nvra.pdf">National Voter Registration form</a> will need to be mailed to your local city or town hall.</p>
